"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-lifestyle-celeb-news-local-celebs-fourth-fastest-man-world-south-africa-akani-simbine-paris-olympics-2024-result\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6633434207165675, \"rank\": 0.49221186528771016, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbLifestyle\\u00bbCeleb News\\u00bbLocal Celebs\\u00bbFourth-fastest man in the world: Meet SA's Akani Simbine  Five things to know about South Africa's Akani Simbine who finished in fourth place in the men's 100m final at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6633434207165675, \"rank\": 0.49221186528771016, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}, {\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.05257608103833e-12, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa'sAkani Simbinefinished in fourth place in the final of the men's100mat theParis Olympicson Sunday, 4 August.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here areFIVEthings to know aboutthe fourth-fastest man in the world.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simbine narrowly missed out on the bronze medal third spot in the final of the men's\\u00a0100min Paris on Sunday.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999872671, \"rank\": 1.255354703455033e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished in\\u00a09.82 which was a new South African record.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fred Kerley from the United States finished in third place, clocking 9.81 - that's how close Simbine was to the podium.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999498436978156, \"rank\": 4.88648787411506e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As previously reported byThe South African, AmericanNoah Lylestook the gold medal in a personal best of 9.79 ahead of Jamaica'sKishane Thompson(9.79).\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999997719364988, \"rank\": 2.280229969758816e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.7202004147064339, \"rank\": 0.38850239356745386, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  Completing the 100m final at 9.82 set a new South African record.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was Akani Simbine's third consecutive Olympic men's 100m final.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been dubbed the most consistent sprinter in the world since the Rio Games in 2016, where he finished fifth in 9.94.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, at the Tokyo Olympics, he finished in fourth place with 9.94.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year in Paris he finished fourth again, this time in 9.82.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999872671, \"rank\": 1.255354703455033e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simbine said that he was happy to have set a South African record and he is not yet done with the sport.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained that he started sprinting late in life and he still wants to get more out of it.\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy to have got a national record, I am happy to have been in the final.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy to be the fourth fastest man in the world and I am happy to have raced in three Olympics finals.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I saw my time it consoled me.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No way am I leaving the sport now.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I started it very late in my life and I still want to get more out of the sport,\\\" he said according toTeam SA.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8880196773240423e-18, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The South African star is 30-years-old and says that he is the fastest he has ever been in his life.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am now 30 and running the fastest I ever have done in my life.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Between Fred and me there was 0.01 seconds.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What more can I ask from myself to run faster than ever before?\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in the race right until the end.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My coach and I have been working hard to make myself faster, to be in the fight for medals,\\\" Akani Simbine said according toTeam SA.\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}, {\"begin\": 2646, \"end\": 2648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8880196773240423e-18, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or by emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.comor sending a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2764, \"end\": 2772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9827991931936751, \"rank\": 0.017501852795200747, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South Africa